  <h3>Why It Worked:</h3>
  <p>Because we didn’t just ask, “What do you want to build?”</p>
  <p>We asked, “What happens if this doesn’t scale?”</p>
  <p>And then we built it to scale.</p>
  <p>No rush jobs. No lock-in. No waiting for someone else to figure it out.</p>

